root: ^To move left, press the left arrow key. To move right, press the right arrow key. To cast your line, use the space bar.
^Your new power over the tides is one of ease; no action on your part is needed to activate it. It will automatically activate when you are in the water and will serve to make fish easier to catch.
^When you do, the magic I have given you for the power over the tides will tell me where you are, and I will soon arrive.
^Thank you for your help. Good luck.
